dct_description_sm: Believed to have been published in James Wallis and Samuel Augustus Oddy's "A general atlas of the world: containing distinct maps of all the principal empires, states, kingdoms, and principalities, throughout the world". London: J. Wallis, 1813.
Inset map: Suppliment [sic] of the Islands of of [sic] the Azores & Cape Verd.
